commit.message:
[PATCH] Remove redundant wheel dep from pyproject.toml

Remove the redundant `wheel` dependency, as it is added by the backend
automatically.  Listing it explicitly in the documentation was
a historical mistake and has been fixed since, see:
https://github.com/pypa/setuptools/commit/f7d30a9529378cf69054b5176249e5457aaf640a

Manually increment version in setup.py

AutoPub's version incrementing logic apparently needs to be adjusted to
handle this type of version number definition.
Automate PyPI package publication via AutoPub
